def maximize_mex_after_queries(q, x, queries):
    y = [0] / x
    mex = 0
    results = []
    for query in queries:
        p = query % x
        y[p] += 1
        while y[mex % x] > mex // x:
            mex += 1
        results.append(mex)
    return results
